EXP1 — wind-direction bias check
================================================================
mean err_x = 10.5 [7.6, 13.4]  px
mean err_y = 4.7 [2.0, 7.5]  px
H0: mean err_x = 0  →  t = +7.035,  p = 0.0000
H0: mean err_y = 0  →  t = +3.356,  p = 0.0011

WIND_VEC in config is approximately (+0.06, +0.02) — downwind = +x mostly.
If estimate is downwind of true source, err_x = est_x − src_x should be > 0.

